      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech的HIPAA合规系统画一个OAuth 2.0授权流程图。核心是从HIPAA_Vault开始，经过EMR_Sync做登录，再到LabAnalyzer获取访问令牌。",
