    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先把HIPAA_Vault和EMR_Sync之间的登录关系画出来。这里LabAnalyzer出现两次，是同一个服务还是不同阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
