      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是同一个服务，但分两个阶段：第一次LabAnalyzer接收令牌，第二次它带着令牌和请求再次发起调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了HIPAA_Vault到EMR_Sync的登录箭头，以及EMR_Sync到第一个LabAnalyzer的访问令牌传递。现在需要处理第二次LabAnalyzer的调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二次LabAnalyzer要把Token和Request一起发给EMR_Sync做权限检查。这里EMR_Sync需要变成一个判断节点，根据scope是否合法分流到PatientRecords或者拒绝。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
