      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：EMR_Sync既是接收登录的节点，又是检查scope的判断节点？我需要把它做成菱形决策形状。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，EMR_Sync在这个流程里承担双重角色。判断通过走Yes分支到PatientRecords，不通过走No分支回到LabAnalyzer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
